---
title: Melty Red Pepper & Chicken Panini with Sweet Potato Wedges & Pesto Mayo
description: When you’re pressed for time, there’s really nothing better than panini sandwiches. This version features double deliciousness with roasted bell pepper and a creamy roasted red pepper spread—but that’s not all! Sautéed zucchini and herbaceous pesto mayo are tucked in too, melded together with mozzarella between golden slices of sourdough. Roasted sweet potato wedges are served on the side with extra pesto mayo, and it all comes together in about 30 minutes. Yay for speedy panini!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64932bae4b18c31a619ff70c-c5ebe0a7.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64932bae4b18c31a619ff70c.pdf
